OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FDonald Trump and Benjamin Netanyahu
OL,7,Fspoke by phone on Sunday amid growing
OL,8,Freports that the US and Israel are
OL,9,Fconsidering resuming attacks on Iran.
OL,11,FThe two leaders talked about Iran
OL,12,Ftogether, on the same day Israeli
OL,13,FPrime Minister Netanyahu held a
OL,14,Fsecurity meeting with his cabinet,
OL,15,FIsraeli media reports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
