OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FThe nation is coordinating with the US
OL,7,Fabout a possible resumption of the war
OL,8,Fon Iran, two people familiar with the
OL,9,Fsituation, including an Israeli
OL,10,Fmilitary officer, told AP on the
OL,11,Fcondition of anonymity.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSpeaking to his Cabinet, Netanyahu
OL,19,Fsaid "our eyes are also open" when it
OL,20,Fcomes to Iran, and said he was
OL,21,F"prepared for any scenario".
OL,26,@{D@FOU{D@]O]
