OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FUS President Trump wrote "for Iran,
OL,7,Fthe clock is ticking" in a Truth
OL,8,FSocial post later on Sunday.
OL,10,F"They better get moving, FAST, or
OL,11,Fthere won't be anything left of them.
OL,12,FTIME IS OF THE ESSENCE!" Trump said.
OL,14,FTrump also posted an AI-generated
OL,15,Fimage of himself surrounded by naval
OL,16,Fships warning of the "calm before the
OL,17,Fstorm" on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
