OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779102176
OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FThe leaders' call comes as a drone
OL,7,Fstruck a an electricity generator
OL,8,Foutside the inner perimeter of Barakah
OL,9,FNuclear Power Plant, in the United
OL,10,FArab Emirates, on Sunday, sparking a
OL,11,Ffire on the site.
OL,13,FNo one immediately claimed
OL,14,Fresponsibility for the strike, which
OL,15,Fthe UAE foreign ministry described as
OL,16,Fan "unprovoked terrorist attack" in a
OL,17,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779102176
OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FThe ministry went on to say the attack
OL,7,Fwas a "dangerous escalation, an
OL,8,Funacceptable act of aggression, and a
OL,9,Fdirect threat to the country's
OL,10,Fsecurity" and asserted the nation's
OL,11,Fright to protect itself against "any
OL,12,Fthreats, allegations, or hostilities".
OL,14,FThere were no reports of injuries or
OL,15,Fradiological release.
OL,17,FThe $20 billion Barakah nuclear power
OL,18,Fplant was built by the UAE with the
OL,19,Fhelp of South Korea, and is the only
OL,20,Fnuclear power plant in the Arab world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
