OL,3,CTrump tells Iran 'clock is ticking'
OL,4,Cafter phone call with Netanyahu
OL,6,FIt can provide a quarter of the energy
OL,7,Fneeds in the UAE, and this is the
OL,8,Ffirst time it has been targeted in the
OL,9,FUS-Israeli conflict in Iran.
OL,11,FThe UAE Defense Ministry said three
OL,12,Fdrones had come over its western
OL,13,Fborder with Saudi Arabia, with the
OL,14,Fother two intercepted.
OL,16,FThe United Nations' nuclear watchdog,
OL,17,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency,
OL,18,Fsaid the strike caused a fire in an
OL,19,Felectrical generator and one reactor
OL,20,Fwas being powered by emergency diesel
OL,21,Fgenerators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
